ygData.messageBody:
Currently i am a level 18 Dark Elf named Damatar on Fennin Ro... i read a post about someone knowing a GREAT spot and that he was going to level there fast from 20 to 24 in one weekend or something and he would tell where it was when he got done leveling .. on monday but this was like 2 weeks ago and i must of deleted the post because i never found out where this golden spot was anyone that read the post or the person who posted it would like to repeat... please tell and if this information cannot be found is there any suggestions on where i should solo and will level fast or somewhere where i can group and level fast? thanks

Damatar 18th circle
Fennin Ro
